---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayoutCa.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="AI Clinical Assistant, MedMe Health"
  description="Captures every consult and drafts the documentation, so the chart is done when the appointment is done. Up to 15 minutes back per consult for your pharmacists."
  showAnnouncement={false}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en-ca" href="https://medmehealth.com/ca/platform/ai-clinical-assistant" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en-ca" href="https://medmehealth.com/ca/" />
  </Fragment>

<style>

  /* ============================================================
     AI CLINICAL ASSISTANT product page. Hero shows the live
     scribe panel (timer + microphone + animated soundwave +
     Pause Scribe state). The Pause Scribe element is rendered
     as a <div> not a <button> so reviewers don't expect it to
     be interactive on the live page (Audrey #206).

     Section flow: hero, trust band, what it does (3 cards),
     services covered (chips), use cases (6 cards), what sets
     it apart (template library + pharmacist help), pharmacist
     stays in control band, navy closing CTA.

     Copy / accuracy edits applied from 2026-06-15 review:
     #207, #208, #210 (uptime in partial), #211, #212, #213,
     #214, #215, #216, #217, #218, #219, #220, #233, #234.
     ============================================================ */

  /* ====== SUB-HERO ============================================= */
  .sub-hero { background: var(--seashell); padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3.5rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .sub-hero__inner { max-width: var(--container); margin: 0 auto; padding-inline: var(--tile-pad-x); position: relative; }
  .sub-hero__bg { position: relative; max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .sub-hero__text { text-align: center; max-width: 820px; margin: 2.5rem auto 0; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .sub-hero h1.h-display { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.4vw, 54px); line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.028em; margin: 0.75rem auto 1rem; text-align: center; text-wrap: balance; }
  .sub-hero h1.h-display .accent { color: var(--matcha); }
  .sub-hero__lede { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.55; color: rgba(6, 62, 84, 0.72); margin: 0 auto 1.75rem; max-width: 720px; }
  .sub-hero__cta { display: inline-flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  @media (max-width: 980px) { .sub-hero__text { margin-top: 2rem; } }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .sub-hero__text { margin-top: 1.5rem; } }

  /* ====== CLINICAL ASSISTANT MOCKUP (animated scribe panel) ====
     Pause Scribe element is a <div> not a <button> so it does
     not read as clickable when viewing the live page. */
  .cwks-stage { display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 24px 12px 40px; }
  .cwks-scribe {
    width: 460px;
    max-width: 100%;
    color: var(--seashell);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }
  .cwks-scribe__title {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--seashell);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    letter-spacing: -0.012em;
  }
  .cwks-scribe__panel {
    background: #1E465D;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 18px 20px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .cwks-scribe__top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .cwks-scribe__time {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--seashell);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .cwks-scribe__mic { width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--seashell); opacity: 0.85; }
  .cwks-scribe__mic svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; }
  .cwks-scribe__wave {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    gap: 2.4px;
    height: 56px;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span {
    width: 5px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,
                  var(--matcha) 0%,
                  var(--matcha) 65%,
                  rgba(195, 196, 48, 0.45) 100%);
    border-radius: 2.4px;
    transform-origin: bottom center;
    animation: cwks-wave 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(1)  { height: 34px; animation-delay: 0s;     }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(2)  { height: 37px; animation-delay: 0.04s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(3)  { height: 53px; animation-delay: 0.08s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(4)  { height: 42px; animation-delay: 0.12s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(5)  { height: 31px; animation-delay: 0.16s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(6)  { height: 24px; animation-delay: 0.20s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(7)  { height: 20px; animation-delay: 0.24s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(8)  { height: 16px; animation-delay: 0.28s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(9)  { height: 14px; animation-delay: 0.32s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(10) { height: 9px;  animation-delay: 0.36s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(11) { height: 5px;  animation-delay: 0.40s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(12) { height: 3px;  animation-delay: 0.44s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(13) { height: 5px;  animation-delay: 0.48s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(14) { height: 2px;  animation-delay: 0.52s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(15) { height: 8px;  animation-delay: 0.56s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(16) { height: 6px;  animation-delay: 0.60s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(17) { height: 9px;  animation-delay: 0.64s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(18) { height: 15px; animation-delay: 0.68s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(19) { height: 6px;  animation-delay: 0.72s; margin-left: 36px; }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(20) { height: 4px;  animation-delay: 0.76s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(21) { height: 8px;  animation-delay: 0.80s;  }
  .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(22) { height: 2px;  animation-delay: 0.84s;  }
  @keyframes cwks-wave {
    0%, 100% { transform: scaleY(0.35); opacity: 0.65; }
    50%      { transform: scaleY(1);    opacity: 1;    }
  }
  /* Pause Scribe state, rendered non-interactive (#206). */
  .cwks-scribe__state {
    background: #92A054;
    color: var(--seashell);
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    text-align: center;
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .cwks-scribe__wave span { animation: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .cwks-scribe { width: 100%; padding: 20px; }
    .cwks-scribe__title { font-size: 18px; }
    .cwks-scribe__time { font-size: 24px; }
    .cwks-scribe__wave { height: 48px; }
    .cwks-scribe__wave span:nth-child(19) { margin-left: 24px; }
  }

  /* ====== LIGHT CARD GRID (3 core capabilities) ================ */
  .light-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
  @media (max-width: 1000px) { .light-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .light-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid rgba(6,62,84,0.08); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.75rem; transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease; }
  .light-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: rgba(6,62,84,0.18); }
  .light-card__icon { display: inline-flex; width: 44px; height: 44px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: rgba(195, 196, 48, 0.14); border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .light-card__icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; stroke: var(--matcha); fill: none; stroke-width: 2; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
  .light-card h3 { margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--indigo); letter-spacing: -0.012em; }
  .light-card p { margin: 0; color: rgba(6,62,84,0.72); line-height: 1.55; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  /* ====== SERVICE CHIPS (where Clinical Assistant operates) ====
     Explicit 4-column grid at desktop so 7 chips land as 4 + 3
     across two rows. Falls back to wrap at narrower viewports. == */
  .svc-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, max-content);
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem 1rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .svc-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, max-content); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .svc-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, max-content); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    .svc-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; justify-items: center; }
  }
  .svc-chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 62, 84, 0.1);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--indigo);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    transition: border-color 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
  }
  .svc-chip:hover { border-color: var(--matcha); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .svc-chip::before {
    content: "";
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--matcha);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ====== USE-CASE DARK CARD GRID ============================== */
  .use-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .use-card {
    background: var(--indigo);
    color: var(--seashell);
    border: 1px solid rgba(195,196,48,0.18);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(6,62,84,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }
  .use-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: var(--matcha); box-shadow: 0 16px 38px rgba(6,62,84,0.16); }
  .use-card__check {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--matcha);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }
  .use-card__check svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; stroke: var(--indigo); fill: none; stroke-width: 3; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
  .use-card h4 { margin: 0 0 0.35rem; font-size: 1.025rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--seashell); letter-spacing: -0.012em; }
  .use-card p { margin: 0; color: rgba(250,249,245,0.72); line-height: 1.5; font-size: 0.875rem; }

  /* ====== SETS-IT-APART (Template library + pharmacist help) === */
  .apart-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .apart-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .apart-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 62, 84, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .apart-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: rgba(6, 62, 84, 0.18); }
  .apart-card__stat {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--matcha);
    letter-spacing: -0.022em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .apart-card h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--indigo);
    letter-spacing: -0.014em;
  }
  .apart-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(6, 62, 84, 0.72);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ====== MATCHA CALLOUT BAND (Pharmacist stays in control) ==== */
  .ctrl-band { background: rgba(195, 196, 48, 0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(195, 196, 48, 0.22); border-radius: 24px; padding: 2.5rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .ctrl-band::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 220px; height: 220px;
    background: var(--matcha);
    opacity: 0.1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .ctrl-band { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 1.75rem; text-align: left; }
  }
  .ctrl-band__text { max-width: 720px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .ctrl-band__kicker { font-size: 11px; color: var(--matcha); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; }
  .ctrl-band h3 { margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--indigo); letter-spacing: -0.018em; }
  .ctrl-band p { margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.55; color: rgba(6,62,84,0.78); text-wrap: pretty; }
  .ctrl-band__cta { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
</style>

<!-- ============= 1. SUB-HERO (live Clinical Assistant scribe panel) ============= -->
<section class="sub-hero" aria-label="Hero">
  <div class="sub-hero__inner">
    <div class="sub-hero__bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="cwks-stage">
        <div class="cwks-scribe" role="img" aria-label="Clinical Assistant is recording. 15 seconds elapsed. Soundwave active.">
          <div class="cwks-scribe__panel">
            <div class="cwks-scribe__top">
              <span class="cwks-scribe__time">00:15</span>
              <span class="cwks-scribe__mic" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/>
                  <path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/>
                  <line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/>
                  <line x1="8" y1="23" x2="16" y2="23"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="cwks-scribe__wave" aria-hidden="true">
              <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
              <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
              <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
              <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-hero__text">
      <h1 class="h-display">The note finishes itself.<br><span class="accent">So your pharmacist doesn't have to.</span></h1>
      <p class="sub-hero__lede">Captures every consult and drafts the documentation as it happens. Pharmacists get up to 15 minutes back per appointment, and the chart is done when the patient walks out, no after-hours catch-up.</p>
      <div class="sub-hero__cta">
        <a class="pill pill--solid" href="/ca/contact">Book a demo <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============= 2. WHAT IT DOES (3 cards) ============= -->
<section class="tile tile--light" aria-label="What the Clinical Assistant does">
  <div class="tile__inner">
    <div class="tile__head">
      <span class="kicker">What It Does</span>
      <h2 class="h-display">Captures the consult.<br>Drafts the note. Pharmacist signs.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Clinical Assistant runs in the background of every appointment. It captures the conversation, structures it into a draft note, and populates the documentation form on demand. The pharmacist reviews, edits, and signs, without re-typing what they just said out loud.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="light-grid">
      <article class="light-card">
        <span class="light-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="8" y1="23" x2="16" y2="23"/></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Listens</h3>
        <p>Captures the consult accurately, with vocabulary tuned to pharmacy practice and clinical workflows. Works for in-person consults and phone follow-ups.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="light-card">
        <span class="light-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Drafts</h3>
        <p>Turns the conversation into a structured draft note as the appointment moves, ready to drop into whichever documentation form fits the service.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="light-card">
        <span class="light-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="9" y1="13" x2="15" y2="13"/><line x1="9" y1="17" x2="15" y2="17"/></svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Auto-fills with one click</h3>
        <p>One click populates the documentation form. The pharmacist reviews, edits, and signs in seconds, not after hours.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============= 3. SERVICES COVERED (chip row) ============= -->
<section class="tile tile--light tile--alt" aria-label="Supported pharmacy services">
  <div class="tile__inner">
    <div class="tile__head">
      <span class="kicker">Built For Every Service Type</span>
      <h2 class="h-display">From minor ailments to medication reviews,<br>one Clinical Assistant for every service.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Tuned for pharmacy practice across the services your team already delivers. Works in-person and on phone follow-ups, with vocabulary, drugs, and clinical entities recognized out of the box. Pharmacists can also use it for hands-free dictation between appointments.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-row">
      <span class="svc-chip">Minor ailments</span>
      <span class="svc-chip">Medication reviews</span>
      <span class="svc-chip">Pharmacist prescribing</span>
      <span class="svc-chip">Health screenings</span>
      <span class="svc-chip">Point-of-care testing</span>
      <span class="svc-chip">Med Sync programs</span>
      <span class="svc-chip">Travel consults</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============= 4. USE CASES (6 dark cards) ============= -->
<section class="tile tile--navy" aria-label="Clinical Assistant use cases">
  <div class="tile__inner">
    <div class="tile__head">
      <span class="kicker">Clinical Assistant Use Cases</span>
      <h2 class="h-display">Six places it lifts the load,<br>so your pharmacist stays with the patient.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Clinical Assistant slots into the pharmacy workflow wherever a pharmacist would otherwise be re-typing what they just said out loud, beyond just billable documentation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="use-grid">
      <article class="use-card">
        <span class="use-card__check" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h4>Clinical assessment documentation</h4>
          <p>SOAP-style notes drafted from the consult. Pharmacist edits the draft, not the blank page.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="use-card">
        <span class="use-card__check" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h4>Phone consultations and dictation</h4>
          <p>Hands-free dictation for phone follow-ups and between-appointment notes, captured straight into the chart.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="use-card">
        <span class="use-card__check" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h4>Prescriber communication summaries</h4>
          <p>Therapy updates, side-effect escalations, and other prescriber-facing summaries drafted from the visit transcript.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="use-card">
        <span class="use-card__check" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h4>Screenshot context to form</h4>
          <p>Drop in a screenshot of an insurance card, fax, or referral, and Clinical Assistant pulls the data into the right fields.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="use-card">
        <span class="use-card__check" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h4>Medication-error or incident reporting</h4>
          <p>Capture the incident as it is discussed, structure it for the reporting form, ready for pharmacist review.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="use-card">
        <span class="use-card__check" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h4>Follow-up plans and care-gap closure</h4>
          <p>Next-step plans, patient-facing action items, and care-gap follow-ups drafted from the visit, ready for review and send.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============= 5. WHAT SETS IT APART (template library + pharmacist help) ============= -->
<section class="tile tile--light tile--alt" aria-label="What sets it apart">
  <div class="tile__inner">
    <div class="tile__head">
      <span class="kicker">What Sets It Apart</span>
      <h2 class="h-display">A scribe that already knows<br>your service catalog.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Other scribes start from a blank slate. Clinical Assistant ships with a pharmacy-specific template library and a real human team behind it, so the draft note matches your workflow on day one.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="apart-grid">
      <article class="apart-card">
        <div class="apart-card__stat">100+</div>
        <h3>Pharmacy-specific template library</h3>
